Type of Feat: Class
Specifics: Beginning at 8th level, once per day the forest master may sink roots into the ground. While rooted, the forest master gains fast healing 5, but has an effective Dexterity score of 1 and may not move from the spot in which he stands or the effect ends. Deep roots will last for 48 hours or until you move one foot or more from where you used the ability.
Use: Selected.